Installation :

    git clone git@github.com:artmees/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks :
    
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Add the appropriate .bash on the machine :

    MAC OS X :
        ln -s ~/.bash_profile ~/.vim/dotfiles/mac_bash_profile
    Linux ( vagrant , ubuntu_home , etc.)
        ln -s ~/.bashrc ~/.vim/dotfiles/filename

Initalizing Submodules Plugins :

    cd ~/.vim/
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
